# Server API conventions

- Validate request bodies with Zod (`server/utils/schemas.ts`).
- Use `useSupabaseAdmin()` for DB/storage writes on intake and admin APIs.
- Use `createError({ statusCode, statusMessage })` with human-readable messages (415/413 for bad uploads).
- Return consistent JSON shapes; document new fields in types under `types/`.

Prefer extending existing utils (`requireInvite`, `storageUpload`, `docxBuilder`) over duplicating logic in route handlers.
